{"tid":2119073,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"擺明有骨-港普F4誕生 蔡少芬鬧姊妹死八婆","createTime":"2020-07-22T01:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T02:27:22.000Z","uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"843d9c57fb249fe601687328d18d7168a25bb8a6","tid":2119073,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T01:52:00.000Z","msg":"4位「凍齡女神」蔡少芬（Ada）、朱茵、陳法蓉（Monica）及洪欣，曾憑港式口音的普通話（港普）鬧出不少笑料，成功在觀眾心目中留下印象。為了延續「港普」傳奇，她們宣布正式組成全新女團「港普F4」，希望透過特色口音繼續發放歡樂！早前她們齊齊受訪，洪欣爆料：「<span class=\"red\">Ada嘅口頭禪係叫個個都係『死八婆』，我哋冇名(口架)，有時都唔知佢叫邊個。</span>」<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">(我真係恭喜你啊，簽左個洪欣咁蠢既西．．．西女人返去！ 恭喜你快撚D捧紅佢添呀！)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於Ada表示好友相處之道，最重要有大方無私的心：「<span class=\"red\">我哋4個有樣嘢好，就係都想大家過得好</span>，(<strong><span class=\"large\">你對邊個好？你對Ada（蔡少芬）唔好咩？</span></strong>)例如呢個廣告接唔到，Pass畀對方都開心，<span class=\"red\">唔會覺得你搶咗我工作，唔會有心病。</span><span class=\"large\"><strong>(成街人都睇死你開公司，仲開戲畀佢拍哦。咁多聯絡？咁唔使請野啦!)</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6PzfKDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6PzfKDH.jpg&h=6660ce41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成班妹珠，明串李嘉欣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XamayxZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXamayxZ.gif&h=593de76f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfe9f6d71d7c5c2814b464a8d3edbac799570fbf","tid":2119073,"uid":281492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"費事嘈..."},{"pid":"132e8d03b8d827e204b8e344fa9cdf23b4475d52","tid":2119073,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:08:25.000Z","msg":"真係4個都八婆樣<br />\n蔡同朱後生都好靚<br />\n而家不了"},{"pid":"98db99db427010ba368933ae86c755006d1963b1","tid":2119073,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T02:20:49.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係個個都叫西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 